rComments: Mariia is a wonderful professor and a rare find. Accessible out of class time, she really dedicates her time for her students and wants everyone to do well. Her course consisted of many online quizzes, participation marks (easy in-class reflections), one research paper, and 2 smaller papers. Good mark achievable if you put the effort. TAKE HER.
